name: Obsidian「黑曜石」
author: PixelOmer
description: The universal package list exporter This is a tweak that allows you to export your package list from Sileo, Zebra and Cydia. All you need to do is tapping the share button in the "Installed Packages" section of your package manager.「通用软件包列表导出器这是一项调整，可让您从Sileo，Zebra和Cydia导出软件包列表。」
